	(451, 4, 'S', 999, 887, 'A', '', 'http://www.youtube.com/v/UMjMDxPkXkI?fs=1&hl=en_US', '', 'You Are God Alone (Not A God)\r\n\r\n\r\nChorus 1\r\nYou are God alone\r\nFrom before time began\r\nYou were on Your throne\r\nYou were God alone\r\nAnd right now\r\nIn the good times and bad\r\nYou are on Your throne\r\nYou are God alone\r\nYou\'re unchangeable\r\nYou\'re unshakable\r\nYou\'re unstoppable\r\nThat\'s what You are\r\nYou\'re unchangeable\r\nYou\'re unshakable\r\nYou\'re unstoppable\r\nThat\'s what You are\r\n\r\n\r\nVerse 1\r\nYou are not a god created\r\nBy human hands\r\nYou are not a god dependent\r\nOn any mortal man\r\nYou are not a god in need of\r\nAnything we can give\r\nBy Your plan\r\nThat\'s just the way it is\r\n\r\n\r\nVerse 2\r\nYou\'re the only God whose power\r\nNone can contend\r\nYou\'re the only God\r\nWhose name and praise will never end\r\nYou\'re the only God who\'s worthy\r\nOf ev\'rything we can give\r\nYou are God\r\nThat\'s just the way it is\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCCLI Song No. 4243463\r\nÃ?Â© 2004 Billy Foote Music | Integrity\'s Hosanna! Music (Admin. by Integrity Music, Inc.) | \r\nBilly Foote | Cindy Foote\r\nFor use solely with the SongSelect Terms of Use.  All rights Reserved. www.ccli.com\r\nCCLI License No. 218004\r\n'),
	(451, 5, 'S', 999, 191, 'A', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/v/cKLQ1td3MbE', '', '~Verse 1\r\nThe splendor of the King\r\nClothed in majesty\r\nLet all the earth rejoice\r\nAll the earth rejoice\r\n\r\n\r\n~Verse 2\r\nHe wraps Himself in light\r\nAnd darkness tries to hide\r\nAnd trembles at His voice\r\nAnd trembles at His voice\r\n\r\n~Verse 3\r\nAnd age to age He stands\r\nAnd time is in His hands\r\nBeginning and the End\r\nBeginning and the End\r\n\r\n~Verse 4\r\nThe Godhead three in one\r\nFather, Spirit, Son\r\nThe Lion and the Lamb\r\nThe Lion and the Lamb\r\n\r\n~Verse 5\r\nHow great is our God\r\nSing with me\r\nHow great is our God\r\nAnd all will see how great\r\nHow great is our God\r\n\r\n~Verse 6\r\nName above all names\r\nWorthy of all praise\r\nMy heart will sing\r\nHow great is our God\r\n\r\n~Verse 8\r\nThen sings my soul,\r\n My Savior God, to Thee;\r\nHow great Thou art, \r\nHow great Thou art;\r\n'),
