	(594, 1, 'S', 999, 917, 'A', '', 'http://www.youtube.com/v/Lk8ue3qN0hg', '', 'White Flag\r\n\r\n\r\nVerse 1\r\nThe battle rages on\r\nAs storm and tempest roar\r\nWe cannot win this fight\r\nInside our rebel hearts\r\nWe\'re laying down our weapons now\r\n\r\n\r\nChorus 1\r\nWe raise our white flag\r\nWe surrender all to You\r\nAll for You\r\nWe raise our white flag\r\nThe war is over\r\nLove has come Your love has won\r\n\r\n\r\nVerse 2\r\nHere on this holy ground\r\nYou made a way for peace\r\nLaying Your body down\r\nYou took our rightful place\r\nThis freedom song is marching on\r\n\r\n\r\nMisc 1\r\n(BRIDGE)\r\nWe lift the cross\r\nLift it high lift it high\r\nWe lift the cross\r\nLift it high lift it high\r\nWe lift the cross\r\nLift it high lift it high\r\nWe lift the cross\r\nLift it high lift it high\r\n(REPEAT)\r\n\r\nCCLI Song # 6223508\r\nChris Tomlin | Jason Ingram | Matt Maher | Matt Redman\r\nÃ?Â© 2012 sixsteps Music/worshiptogether.com songs/Vamos Publishing/Said and Done Music/Thankyou Music/Valley Of Songs Music/Worship Together Music/Six Steps BMI Designee (all admin. by EMI Christian Music Publishing); Sony/ATV Timber Publishing/West Main Music/Windsor Hill Music (all admin. by Sony/ATV Sounds LLC). For use solely with the SongSelect Terms of Use.  All rights reserved. www.ccli.com\r\nCCLI License # 218004\r\n'),
