	(594, 4, 'S', 999, 861, 'D', '', 'http://www.youtube.com/v/RtdkMAx8GDg&hl=en&fs=1&', '', '~Verse 1\r\nEven [D]now He\'s [A/D]waiting for [D]us\r\nTo [Em]fall on our knees and [A]worship\r\nEven [D]now He\'s [A/D]ready for [D]us\r\nTo [Em]lift up our hands to His [A]name\r\n~Chorus 1\r\nEven [G]now as our [A/G]praises go forth\r\nThe [D/F#]heavens will pour out [G2]on us\r\nAnd His [Em]glory will fill this [A]place\r\n1. even [D]now (Verse [G2]2)[A]\r\n2. even [D]now (Inst)[Asus]\r\n3. even [C/D]now (Chorus [D]2)\r\n~Verse 2\r\nEven [D]now He\'s [A/D]waiting for [D]us\r\nTo [Em]fall on our faces and [A]worship\r\nEven [D]now He\'s [A/D]ready for [D]us\r\nTo [Em]offer that sweet sacri - [A]fice (Chorus 1)\r\n~Chorus 2\r\nEven [G]now as our [A/G]praises go forth\r\nThe [D/F#]heavens will pour out [G2]on us\r\nAnd His [Em]glory will fill this [A]place\r\nAnd His [Em]glory will fill this [A]place\r\nWe need Your [Em]glory in this [Asus]place\r\nEven [D]now\r\n'),
	(594, 5, 'S', 999, 732, 'D', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/v/lqFOsOPj9uk', '', '~Verse 1\r\nMy Jesus, I love Thee, \r\nI know Thou art mine-\r\nFor Thee all the follies \r\nOf sin I resign;\r\n\r\n\r\n~Verse 3\r\nI love Thee because \r\nThou hast first loved me.\r\nAnd purchased my pardon\r\n On Calvary\'s tree;\r\n\r\n\r\n~Verse 4\r\nI\'ll love Thee in life, \r\nI will love Thee in death,\r\nAnd praise Thee as long as \r\nThou lendest me breath;\r\n   \r\n\r\n~Verse 5\r\nIn mansions of glory \r\nAnd endless delight,\r\nI\'ll ever adore Thee \r\nIn heaven so bright;\r\n\r\n~Verse 6\r\nI\'ll sing with the glittering\r\n Crown on my brow,\r\n"If ever I loved Thee, \r\nMy Jesus, \'tis now."\r\n\r\n~Verse 7\r\nAnd say when the death-dew\r\n Lies cold on my brow,\r\n"If ever I loved, Thee,\r\n My Jesus, \'tis now."\r\n\r\n~Verse 8\r\nI love Thee for wearing \r\nThe thorns on Thy brow:\r\nIf ever I loved Thee, \r\nMy Jesus, \'tis now.\r\n\r\n~Verse 9\r\nMy gracious Redeemer, \r\nMy Savior art Thou;\r\nIf ever I loved Thee, \r\nMy Jesus, \'tis now.\r\n');
