	(148, 'Knowing You (All I Once Held Dear)', 'Graham Kendrick', '~Verse 1\r\nAll I [Am]once held [C]dear, built my [Am]life[G] up[C]on,\r\nAll this [Am]world [C]reveres and [Am]wars to [G]own;\r\nAll I [F]once thought [C]gain I have [F]coun[G]ted [C]loss,\r\nSpent and [Am]worthless [C]now com[Am]pared to [G]this.\r\n~Chorus\r\nKnowing [F]You, [C]Jesus, [F]knowing [C]You\r\nThere [Am]is no [G]greater [F]thing.\r\nYou\'re my [C]all, You\'re the [F]best,\r\nYou\'re my [C]joy, my righteous[F]ness,\r\nAnd I [C]love You [F]Lord.  [C]    [F]\r\n~Verse 2\r\nNow my [Am]heart\'s de[C]sire is to [Am]know [G]You [C]more,\r\nTo be [Am]found in [C]You and [Am]know as [G]Yours,\r\nTo pos[F]sess by [C]faith what I [F]could [G]not [C]earn\r\nAll sur[Am]passing [C]gift of [Am]righteous[G]ness\r\n~Verse 3\r\nOh to [Am]know the [C]power of Your [Am]rise[G]n l[C]ife,\r\nAnd to [Am]know You [C]in Your [Am]suffer[G]ings;\r\nTo [F]become like [C]You in Your [F]death, [G]my [C]Lord,\r\nSo with [Am]You to [C]live and [Am]never [G]die.', '', '1996 Integrity Music, Inc.', 'http://www.youtube.com/v/MGbuz8QuhmE&hl=en&fs=1&', '', 'All I once held dear, built my life upon, All this world reveres and wars to own; All I once thought gain I have counted loss, Spent and worthless now compared to this. Knowing You, Jesus, knowing You There is no greater thing. You\\\'re my all, You\\\'re the best, You\\\'re my joy, my righteousness, And I love You Lord. Now my heart\\\'s desire is to know You more, To be found in You and know as Yours, To possess by faith what I could not earn All surpassing gift of righteousness Oh to know the power of Your risen life, And to know You in Your sufferings; To become like You in Your death, my Lord, So with You to live and never die.'),
	(149, 'Blessed Be The Name Of The Lord', '', '~Verse 1\r\n[F]Blessed be the name of the Lord,\r\n[Bb]Blessed be the name of the Lord,[C]\r\n[F]Blessed be the name of the L[Bb]ord Most [C]Hi[Bb]gh.  (repeat)\r\n~Chorus\r\nThe name of the L[F]ord is----[Bb-F]--------a[Bb] strong [F]tower.[Gm-F]\r\nThe righteous run [C]into [Bb]it and they are [F]save[Bb]d.  (repeat)\r\n~Verse 2\r\n[G]Holy is the name of the Lord,\r\n[C]Holy is the name of the Lord,[D]\r\n[G]Holy is the name of the L[C]ord Most [D]Hig[C]h.  (repeat)\r\n~Tag\r\n[G]Holy is the name of the L[C2]ord (3x)  Most H[D]igh.[Csus-G]\r\n', '', '1989 Polygram Int. Publishing & Utterback Music, Inc.', '', '', 'Blessed be the name of the Lord, Blessed be the name of the Lord, Blessed be the name of the Lord Most High.  (repeat) The name of the Lord is------------a strong tower. The righteous run into it and they are saved.  (repeat) Holy is the name of the Lord, Holy is the name of the Lord, Holy is the name of the Lord Most High.  (repeat) Holy is the name of the Lord (3x)  Most High.'),
	(150, 'I Could Sing Of Your Love Forever', 'Martin Smith', '~Verse 1\r\nOver the mountains and the sea,\r\nYour river runs with love for me\r\nAnd I will open up my heart,\r\nAnd let the healer set me free\r\n~Verse 2\r\nI\'m happy to be in the truth,\r\nAnd I will daily lift my hands\r\nFor I will always sing\r\nOf when your love came down.\r\n~Chorus\r\nI could sing of your love forever\r\nI could sing of your love forever\r\nI could sing of your love forever\r\nI could sing of your love forever\r\n~Bridge\r\nOh I feel like dancing,\r\nIt\'s foolishness I know\r\nBut when the world \r\nHas seen the light\r\nThey will dance with joy\r\nLike we\'re dancing now.\r\n', '', '1996 Mercy /Vineyard', 'https://www.youtube.com/v/zeCwwaciAA8', '', '.mysql_real_escape_string(Over the mountains and the sea, Your river runs with love for me And I will open up my heart, And let the healer set me free I\'m happy to be in the truth, And I will daily lift my hands For I will always sing Of when your love came down. I could sing of your love forever I could sing of your love forever I could sing of your love forever I could sing of your love forever Oh I feel like dancing, It\'s foolishness I know But when the world Has seen the light They will dance with joy Like we\'re dancing now.).'),
