	(424, 'We Believe In You', '', '~Intro\r\n[Em] [D] [Em] [D] [Em]\r\n~Verse 1\r\nCome [Em]down from Your holy mountain\r\nLike [D]fire on the land\r\nCome [Em]down from Your holy mountain\r\nAnd [D]take our hand\r\n~Chorus\r\n[G] \'Cause [D]we believe in [C]You\r\n[D]That Your word is [G]true\r\n[D]That You died and [C]rose [G/B]a  -  [C]gain\r\n[G] And [D]we believe Your [C]blood\r\n[D]Covers all our [G]sin\r\n[D]We believe You\'ll [C]come [G/B]a  -  [C]gain\r\nJesus come again\r\n', '', ' 1994 Mercy/Vineyard Publishing; ARR; ICS; UBP; ', '', '', 'Come down from Your holy mountain Like fire on the land Come down from Your holy mountain And take our hand \'Cause we believe in You That Your word is true That You died and rose a  -  gain And we believe Your blood Covers all our sin We believe You\'ll come a  -  gain Jesus come again'),
