	(496, 'I Will Worship You Lord', 'Daniel Gardner ', '\r\n~Verse 1\r\nI will worship You Lord \r\nWith all of my might,\r\nI will praise You with a Psalm;\r\nI will worship You Lord\r\nWith all of my might,\r\nI will praise You all day long.\r\n\r\n\r\n~Verse 2\r\nFor Thou O Lord art glorious\r\nAnd Thy name \r\nis greatly to be praised,\r\nMay my heart be pure \r\nand holy in Thy sight,\r\nAs I worship You \r\nwith all of my might.\r\n', '', '1981 Integrity\'s Hosanna Music', '', '', 'I will worship You Lord With all of my might, I will praise You with a Psalm; I will worship You Lord With all of my might, I will praise You all day long. For Thou O Lord art glorious And Thy name is greatly to be praised, May my heart be pure and holy in Thy sight, As I worship You with all of my might.'),
