	(520, 'So You Would Come', 'Russell Fragar', '~Verse 1\r\nBefore the world began,\r\nYou were on His mind;\r\nAnd ev\'ry tear you cry\r\nIs precious in His eyes.\r\nBecause of His great love,\r\nHe gave His only son,\r\nEv\'rything was done,\r\nSo you would come.\r\n\r\n~Verse 2\r\nNothing you can do,\r\nCould make Him love you more;\r\nAnd nothing that you\'ve done\r\nCould make Him close the door.\r\nBecause of His great love,\r\nHe gave His only Son,\r\nEv\'rything was done,\r\nSo you would come.\r\n\r\n~Verse 3\r\nCome to the Father\r\nthough your gift is small,\r\nBroken hearts, broken lives,\r\nHe will take them all.\r\nThe power of the Word,\r\nThe power of His blood,\r\nEv\'rything was done\r\nSo you would come.\r\n', '', '1996 Hillsong Publishing', '', '', 'Before the world began, You were on His mind; And ev\\\'ry tear you cry Is precious in His eyes. Because of His great love, He gave His only son, Ev\\\'rything was done, So you would come. Nothing you can do, Could make Him love you more; And nothing that you\\\'ve done Could make Him close the door. Because of His great love, He gave His only Son, Ev\\\'rything was done, So you would come. Come to the Father though your gift is small, Broken hearts, broken lives, He will take them all. The power of the Word, The power of His blood, Ev\\\'rything was done So you would come.'),
	(521, 'Because We Believe', 'Jamie Harvill & Nancy Gordon', '~Verse 1\r\nMen: We believe in God, the Father.\r\n\r\n~Verse 2\r\nWomen: We believe in God, the Father.\r\n~Verse 3\r\n\r\n     Men: We believe in Christ, the Son,\r\n\r\n~Verse 4\r\nWomen: We believe in Christ, the Son.\r\n\r\n~Verse 6\r\nHoly, holy, holy is our God.\r\nWorthy, worthy, worthy is our King.\r\nAll glory and honor are His to receive;\r\nTo Jesus we sing, because we believe.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n~Verse 7\r\nMen: We believe in the Holy Spirit,\r\n\r\n~Verse 8\r\nWomen: We believe in the Holy Spirit;\r\n~Verse 10\r\nMen: We believe in the Holy Bible.\r\n\r\n~Verse 11\r\nWomen: We believe in the Holy Bible.\r\n~Verse 12\r\n\r\n       Men: We believe in the virgin birth,\r\n\r\n~Verse 13\r\nWomen: We believe in the virgin birth.\r\n~Verse 14\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n~Verse 15\r\nMen: We believe in the blood of Jesus,\r\n', '', ' 1996 Integrity\'s Praise! Music and  Integrity\'s Hosanna! Music', 'http://www.youtube.com/v/0eTxEpHNJh8&hl=en&fs=1&', '', 'Men: We believe in God, the Father. Women: We believe in God, the Father. Men: We believe in Christ, the Son, Women: We believe in Christ, the Son. Holy, holy, holy is our God. Worthy, worthy, worthy is our King. All glory and honor are His to receive; To Jesus we sing, because we believe. Men: We believe in the Holy Spirit, Women: We believe in the Holy Spirit; Men: We believe in the Holy Bible. Women: We believe in the Holy Bible. Men: We believe in the virgin birth, Women: We believe in the virgin birth. Men: We believe in the blood of Jesus,'),
