	(611, 'Jesus Jesus Jesus', 'Debbie Kerner', '~Verse 1\r\nJesus,  Jesus, Jesus, \r\nJesus, Jesus.\r\n~Verse 2\r\nHe died, He died, He died,\r\n He died, He died.\r\n~Verse 4\r\nHe rose, He rose, He rose, \r\nHe rose, He rose.\r\n~Verse 5\r\nHe lives, He lives, He lives,\r\n He lives, He lives.\r\n~Bridge\r\nWe live through Him, We live through Him, \r\nWe live through Him, We live through Him,\r\nWe live through Him.\r\nJesus, Jesus, Jesus, Jesus, Jesus.\r\n', '', '1971 Maranatha! Music', '', '', 'Jesus,  Jesus, Jesus, Jesus, Jesus. He died, He died, He died, He died, He died. He rose, He rose, He rose, He rose, He rose. He lives, He lives, He lives, He lives, He lives. We live through Him, We live through Him, We live through Him, We live through Him, We live through Him. Jesus, Jesus, Jesus, Jesus, Jesus.'),
