	(790, 'For You Are Glorious', 'David W. Morris & Mike Massa ', '\r\n~Verse 1\r\nWe see Jesus,\r\nFor His suff\'ring crowned with glory \r\n	 And with praise,\r\nTasting death for all men by God\'s grace;\r\nGiven pow\'r to put all things in place;\r\n\r\n\r\n~Verse 2\r\nFor You are glorious, shining victorious,\r\nO\'er pow\'rs and principalities,\r\nFor You are glorious, shining victorious,\r\nDisarming all Your enemies\r\nThe rulers of this world, \r\nBeneath Your feet are hurled\r\nAs You reign, our conquering King.\r\n\r\n~Verse 4\r\nAnd we see Jesus,\r\nSeated at the right hand of the throne,\r\nMaking intercession for His own\r\nUpholding all things by His word alone.\r\n', '', ' 1988 Integrity\'s Hosanna! Music ; ', '', '', 'We see Jesus, For His suff\'ring crowned with glory And with praise, Tasting death for all men by God\'s grace; Given pow\'r to put all things in place; For You are glorious, shining victorious, O\'er pow\'rs and principalities, For You are glorious, shining victorious, Disarming all Your enemies The rulers of this world, Beneath Your feet are hurled As You reign, our conquering King. And we see Jesus, Seated at the right hand of the throne, Making intercession for His own Upholding all things by His word alone.'),
